<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heinrich von Absberg zu Rumburg</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Unterstützung wegen des für Montag nach Hilpoltstein erbetenen Geleits für die Nürnberger Gesandten nach Ingolstadt zum Schiedsgericht am kommenden Mittwoch.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_219" id="108r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_219_r1l2"><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Abtſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> cʒü <expan>Runnb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_219_r1l3"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> / Als vvir die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>yecʒunde<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> tag gen <expan>Jngolſt<ex>at</ex></expan> <expan>ſchıcke<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ſülle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l4"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>H<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> Stephan <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd ſeın gnade <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vmb ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l5">geleitte daʒ er ſchıcken vnd <expan>beſtelle<ex>n</ex></expan> wöll / daʒ das bey den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſeÿ auf den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l6">nehſten Montag cʒü nacht cʒüm Stain / . vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / . daʒ Jr das 
<del rend="strikethrough">alſo </del> beſtellen helfft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l7">daʒ das geleitte alſo cʒü den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> kum / als vvir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> des geleittes <expan>vvege<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l8">nehſt hie mit ew auch geredt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . vnd laʒʒet ew das <expan>beuolhe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein / Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_219" id="108r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Abtsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> czü <expan>Runnb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, als wir die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>yeczunde<ex>n</ex></expan> czu <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> tag gen
                                <expan>Ingolst<ex>at</ex></expan>
<expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>sülle<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> Stephan,
                                <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und sein gnade
                                <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> umb sein geleitte, daz er schicken
                        und <expan>bestelle<ex>n</ex></expan> wöll, daz das bey den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sey auf den <app><note><q type="date">nehsten montag</q>27.05.1409</note></app> czü nacht
                        czüm Stain. Und <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir das bestellen
                        helfft, daz das geleitte also czü den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> kum,
                        als wir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> des geleittes <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        nehst hie mit ew auch geredt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, und lazzet ew
                        das <expan>bevolhe<ex>n</ex></expan> sein. Das
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
